     * March 2019 - Postdoctoral fellow in bioinformatics

   The group "Genetics, Epigenetics and biology of sarcomas" (Dir. Franck
   Tirode) is looking for a post-doc in bioinformatics (18 months). The
   project aims at identifying the molecular alterations and defining the
   precise tumor subtype of a large series of “still unclassified”
   sarcomas using multidimensional and integrative data analysis
   approaches.
   More information
